<div id="review_1020420640" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1020420640" />
    <a title="Bookspective" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/29814876-bookspective"><img alt="Bookspective" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1632407293p2/29814876.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1020420640?book_show_action=true">Nov 22, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bookspective" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bookspective" href="/user/show/29814876-bookspective">Bookspective</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/29814876-bookspective?shelf=library">library</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/29814876-bookspective?shelf=sal2021">sal2021</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/29814876-bookspective?shelf=2021">2021</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1020420640" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17854757665166247865">An affluent single mother of two, Aranya Dhari is entangled in a legal feud with her own mother, over their ancestral property to which Aranya has legal rights to and yet left out by her mom. This sums up what the book is about. The book cover, the title and the blurb are so misleading. Between the pages of the book is a paltry attempt at writing a soul stirring family drama but it sadly was just a huge letdown to me.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

